      "content": "Whoa, 95% efficacy? That's a massive number. I was looking at the raw data sheet earlier and the primary endpoint comparison against the placebo group looked pretty flat. Are you sure those numbers are right? Can you walk me through how you arrived at that 95% figure? I need to be able to defend that specifically if the board asks for the p-values.",
